description: This header file defines external function prototypes for the Module Container Object within the ANSC (Advanced Networking Service Container) environment. It includes declarations for functions related to module interface management, state transitions, and control operations.

methods.name: AnscMcoGetQueryIfObject
methods.description: Retrieves the query interface object for the Module Container.

methods.name: AnscMcoIgnite
methods.description: Initializes or activates the Module Container object.

methods.name: AnscMcoPutOut
methods.description: Deactivates or cleans up the Module Container object.

methods.name: AnscMcoSwitch
methods.description: Switches the Module Container on or off based on the boolean parameter.

methods.name: AnscMcoAddModuleIf
methods.description: Adds a module interface with the specified name and handle.

methods.name: AnscMcoDelModuleIf
methods.description: Deletes a module interface by name.

methods.name: AnscMcoQueryModuleIf
methods.description: Queries and retrieves a module interface by name.

methods.name: AnscMcoRegisterIfs
methods.description: Registers interfaces for the Module Container.
